## 🛠️ Project Structure

```
nputop
├── assets/             # Images for documentation
├── nputop/
│   ├── api/            # Ascend NPU APIs & backend
│   ├── gui/            # Interactive UI (GPL-3.0-only)
│   ├── cli.py          # Command-line entry point
│   └── version.py      # Versioning and metadata
